description: Creates a Selenium testing project. Projects are used to track  TestGridSession instances.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: Human-readable name of the Selenium testing project.

parameters.name: vpcConfig
parameters.description: The VPC security groups and subnets that are attached to a project. A list of VPC security group IDs in your Amazon VPC. (string) --- A list of VPC subnet IDs in your Amazon VPC. (string) --- The ID of the Amazon VPC.

nested_params.name: securityGroupIds
nested_params.description: A list of VPC security group IDs in your Amazon VPC.

nested_params.name: subnetIds
nested_params.description: A list of VPC subnet IDs in your Amazon VPC.

nested_params.name: vpcId
nested_params.description: The ID of the Amazon VPC.
